The paper deals with anomaly detection in human actions using pose graphs, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method proposed involves clustering and mixture modeling, which are techniques commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of video sequences, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with anomaly detection, which is a topic in computer security (cs.CR).
